org.safs

Class MatchData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.MatchData

  • public class MatchData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to fill the matches Vector with match data. At each level in the GuiObjectVector, we will store a match if one is found. This happens all the way down to the final GuiTestObject matching the final GuiObjectVector level. Only if there is a match all the way down to the final GuiObjectVector level can we say we have found an object matching the recognition string.
